videos.description: Middle Tennessee's Brandon Walters gets the ball down low and converts the layup for an and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Walters finishes layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Middle Tennessee's Edward Simpson comes away with the steal and sets up Nick King for the emphatic jam in the first half.
videos.headline: Simpson's steal sets up King's slam

videos.description: After initially finding no one open, Middle Tennessee's Tyrik Dixon deflects a pass off a USC defender and converts the mid-range jumper.
videos.headline: Dixon's self-pass sets up jumper

videos.description: USC's Jordan McLaughlin finds Bennie Boatwright in transition for a first-half 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Boatwright knocks down transition 3

videos.description: Middle Tennessee's Nick King takes it to the paint and nails the contested layup.
videos.headline: King converts tough layup

videos.description: After missing his shot attempt, Middle Tennessee's Tyrik Dixon grabs the offensive rebound and converts the layup.
videos.headline: Dixon's rebound sets up second-chance points

videos.description: USC's Bennie Boatwright tries throwing down a dunk but is rejected by Karl Gamble in the second half.
videos.headline: Gamble denies Boatwright's dunk attempt

videos.description: USC's Chimezie Metu calls for ball in the post and finishes the two-handed dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: Metu delivers emphatic slam

videos.description: USC's Shaqquan Aaron dishes the ball to Chimezie Metu down low for the emphatic dunk.
videos.headline: Aaron finds Metu for two-handed jam
